172 A.3d 1082 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. A.A., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-281 September Term 2017

079486 November 09, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003459-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
